# ğŸ’¼ TaxPal â€“ Personal Finance & Tax Estimator for Freelancers

TaxPal is a full-stack web application that helps freelancers and gig workers
track income, manage expenses, plan budgets, and estimate taxes efficiently
through a single, user-friendly platform.

---

## ğŸš€ Project Overview

Freelancers often deal with irregular income, scattered expense records, and
complex tax calculations. TaxPal simplifies personal finance management by
centralizing all financial data and automating budgeting and tax estimation.

This project demonstrates real-world full-stack development skills including
authentication, REST APIs, database design, and responsive UI development.

---

## ğŸ¯ Problem Statement

- No centralized platform for freelance income & expense tracking  
- Difficulty in managing category-wise budgets  
- Manual and error-prone tax estimation  
- Lack of organized financial reports for tax filing  

**TaxPal addresses these challenges** by providing an automated, secure, and
scalable financial management system.

